<br>
Long live The Fellowship and short lived are its foes.<br>
Tacomir Rezzyourazz <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/usingsang.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SingSang</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 454<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(9/10/02 4:14:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=59.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.exodusfellowship.com/Sing-B.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Twilight Sea </span><hr size=1> I have not fought there yet, but will go there soon for the Twilight Armor quests. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#00000F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/bexodusfellowshipforum.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=angeliqe>Angeliqe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 57<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(9/10/02 9:52:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=59.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Twilight Sea </span><hr size=1> Stay away from the island with the shades...I was there recently and saw several green shadow looking creeps on an island.  I figured I'd go have a look and see if they would agro on me....bad idea, hehe.  I probably would have made it back if they weren't chain lifetapping and my computer didn't freeze from all the lag.  I couldn't even hit gate.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I hate greenie deaths.  Their agro range is pretty large and I had quite a few on me even though I only saw one or two. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/uthearrowolfs.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Arrowolfs</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(9/10/02 10:34:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=59.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Twilight Sea </span><hr size=1> I picked up a shadowed once while swimming to Scarlet Desert and got a little too close to the island.  Bad island.  I don't know a lot about the elementals on the elemental island other than I see them all around me when I land at the Twilight teleport point on this island.  I would suggest you checking on their faction before you proceed to kill them, not sure if you take faction hits for them.  <br>
<br>
Also, Rivin was doing some deep sea swimming from elemental island to the Scarlet Desert zone one night and the sea turtles killed him right out of the blue.  So if you're up for a midnight dip, you may want to invis first.<br>
<br>
If we won't lose elemental faction, I'll try to show.  Otherwise, I've found it a safe practice not to kill any of the unaggressive flora or fauna surrounding teleportal points <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Karmyn Arrowolf <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#00000F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/bexodusfellowshipforum.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=angeliqe>Angeliqe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 58<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(9/10/02 2:22:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=59.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Twilight Sea </span><hr size=1> Yes the elementals do give you faction and you can become kos for killing them, but your faction with the island inhabitants (humanoid) goes up. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/uursimajor1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>UrsiMajor1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 355<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(9/11/02 10:51:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=59.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.webdesignbyursula.com/ursi_5.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Twilight Sea </span><hr size=1> Yeah I agree with pretty much everything said here on Twilight.<br>
<br>
Elemental island is a blast and there are some really great common drops off named elementals:<br>
<br>
Fetish of the Nimble/Agile like +5 agi/+10 agi range items<br>
Lesser/Greater Talisman of Wisdom etc. +3 wis/+5 wis neck<br>
<br>
Stay away from the shade spectre island.  I could solo maybe one at level 50 - forget it if there was an add- gate city.<br>
<br>
Also beware of the under water secret entrance near Katta Castellum.  It took the moral support of our guild as well as Xxax- uber rogue from GL with invis/eb items to drag my drowned corpse from by the secret entrance.<br>
<br>
You will be fine swimming from the Scarlet Desert Area or coming from Fungus Grove Area swimming wise. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#00000F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/utacomir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tacomir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(9/11/02 2:10:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=59.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> twilight sea beasties</span><hr size=1> Thanks for the input everyone.  As far as I can make out, the biggest problem is going to be the faction hits.  The Elementals on the island are all under 36 and most are 25 - 30.  I am thinking that a good full group of mid 30's should have no problem.  But a second group of same or higher might be a nice addition for saftey.  I will try to get in touch with everyone while online some time soon and see if we can plan a night to try this out.  <br>
<br>
Long Live Exodus Fellowship and short lived are its foes<br>
<br>
Tacomir Rezzyourazz <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=59.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=59.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=59.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.exodusfellowship.com/add-_reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=59.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.threadControl?topicID=59.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/black_default/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=59.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=59.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub135.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="exodusfellowshipforumfrm6">The Grand Hall<option value="exodusfellowshipforumfrm5">Event Planning<option value="exodusfellowshipforumfrm3">Tales of the Fellowship!<option value="exodusfellowshipforumfrm10">Epic Quests<op